description: Try our easy to follow Tuna Pasta Bake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Pasta bake,Pescatarian,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Zucchini,Fish,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Peanut free
name: Tuna Pasta Bake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500g tuna bake with spinach and garlic

recipeInstructions.text: Cook pasta flowing packet directions. Drain and place into a 1.5 litre capacity greased baking dish.
Spoon flaked tuna and grated zucchini over pasta. Pour Leggo’s Tuna Bake over tuna, zucchini and pasta and gently mix together.
Sprinkle with mozzarella cheese and bake in a preheated oven at 190°C for 20 minutes or until golden brown.
